term: MetricsPort
---
definition:

MetricsPort is a Tor configuration option.
Is used mainly by tor relay operators to read the information sent to Tor Metrics.
This helps to diagnose problems with the relay.

For more information please read the MetricsPort section on the article about [overloaded relays](../../relay-operators/relay-bridge-overloaded/#metricsport).

